# Themes

[![Themes](https://img.shields.io/badge/Themes-3-green)](#themes-list)
[![RusherHack v2.0.6](https://img.shields.io/badge/RusherHack-v2.0.6-purple?logo=data:image/png;base64,)](https://rusherhack.org/changelog.html)

> [!WARNING]
> None of the themes listed here have been verified or confirmed to be safe. Use at your own risk!

> [!IMPORTANT]
> These themes are not affiliated with or endorsed by Rusher Development LLC.

Themes modify RusherHack’s appearance, changing colors, fonts, and UI elements to customize the look and feel of the utility mod.

> [!NOTE]
> Themes are community-created and primarily affect the visual style of RusherHack’s interface, such as the HUD, menus, and click GUI.

## Badge Info

> [!TIP]
> Badges provide quick access to theme resources:
> - **Latest Release**: Links to the theme’s releases page.
> - **Downloads**: Directly downloads the latest theme version.

## Theme List

> [!NOTE]
> The following themes are community contributions. Always verify the source code and test themes in a safe environment before applying them to your main game.
